{% set version = "1.3.2" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-tidyverse
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/tidyverse_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/tidyverse/tidyverse_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 37fbf8b72e49e96b1770dfb8e37f3e9e29269e8d6c96d6d3902561252ec1cf61

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

    - r-hms >=1.0.0
    - r-httr >=1.4.2
    - r-jsonlite >=1.7.2
    - r-lubridate >=1.7.10
    - r-magrittr >=2.0.1
    - r-modelr >=0.1.8
    - r-pillar >=1.6.0
    - r-purrr >=0.3.4
    - r-readr >=1.4.0
    - r-readxl >=1.3.1
    - r-reprex >=2.0.0

    - r-rstudioapi >=0.13
    - r-rvest >=1.0.0
    - r-stringr >=1.4.0
    - r-tibble >=3.1.0
    - r-tidyr >=1.1.3
    - r-xml2 >=1.3.2
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-broom >=0.7.6
    - r-cli >=2.4.0

    - r-googlesheets4 >=0.3.0
    - r-haven >=2.3.1
    - r-hms >=1.0.0
    - r-httr >=1.4.2
    - r-jsonlite >=1.7.2
    - r-lubridate >=1.7.10
    - r-magrittr >=2.0.1
    - r-modelr >=0.1.8
    - r-pillar >=1.6.0
    - r-purrr >=0.3.4
    - r-readr >=1.4.0
    - r-readxl >=1.3.1
    - r-reprex >=2.0.0
    - r-rlang >=0.4.10
    - r-rstudioapi >=0.13
    - r-rvest >=1.0.0
    - r-stringr >=1.4.0
    - r-tibble >=3.1.0
    - r-tidyr >=1.1.3
    - r-xml2 >=1.3.2

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('tidyverse')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('tidyverse')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: http://tidyverse.tidyverse.org, https://github.com/tidyverse/tidyverse
